    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "@vvo Fixed both.\nAbout `hoganCompileOptions`, I strongly disagree since here, this is fairly template engine agnostic, the only part of `instantsearch.js` which knows we're using `Hogan` is the `renderTemplate` function, and I'm pretty sure that if we decided to switch to another templating engine, this `options` parameter would be useful.\n",
